    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-maintained, making it a reliable and stylish choice for your next car. It runs smoothly and looks great, with only minor signs of use that show it's been cared for. Ready to provide many more miles of happy driving, this is a solid investment for anyone looking for quality and value!",
