    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, and while the air conditioning works, the heater can be temperamental. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or parts car. The engine is currently running but is highly unreliable and prone to overheating, while the transmission shows significant slipping in higher gears. The exterior has several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. It will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the paint. The interior shows moderate wear, including some minor stains on the upholstery and signs of use on the controls. All mechanical systems are functional, though the car shows age-related wear.",
      "price": 20000.0,
