    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and comfort without the new-car price tag. The exterior finish still holds a beautiful shine, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use like small stone chips on the front bumper. The alloy wheels are in great shape, and the tires have significant tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept smoke-free. The upholstery is well-preserved, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster, while the dashboard and trim remain free of cracks or fading. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; it has a documented service history and has recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and oil change. It starts eagerly, shifts smoothly, and provides a quiet, confident ride. This is a solid, honest car that has many miles of dependable service left to offer.",
